## Step 3 — Deploy to Vercel

1. Go to **vercel.com** → Sign up/login with your GitHub account
2. Click **Add New Project**
3. Select your `play-reviews-api` repo
4. Leave all settings as default
5. Click **Deploy**

Vercel will build and deploy in about 60 seconds. You'll get a URL like:
```
https://play-reviews-api-yourname.vercel.app
```

**Test it immediately** by visiting this in your browser (replace with your URL):
```
https://play-reviews-api-yourname.vercel.app/api/reviews?appId=com.habitrpg.android.habitica&num=10
